- Install Laravel version 5.8 because that's the version used in our course
    laravel new --5.8
    composer create-project laravel/laravel . "5.8.*"
- Composer will install the specified version in the current directory
- Make sure that there are no files, including hidden Git files, in the directory where we install Laravel
    double shift to search
